{"tid":2084983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知香港同沙特、敍利亞、吉布提、巴林等國有乜共通之處？","createTime":"2020-06-29T15:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T15:28:59.000Z","uid":321059,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2580b534a7051ef2a22a705607000fd21efa259","tid":2084983,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係都係搵同一間公關公司幫佢哋洗底呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港府企圖以「香港重新出發」計劃「洗白」，在林鄭上任特首三周年前夕，政府宣佈計劃合約由Consulum FZ LLC投得，合約價值近5,000萬港元。翻查資料，<span style=\"color: red;\">總部設於英國的Consulum早有為獨裁政權「洗白」的經驗，2018年沙特阿拉伯政權空襲也門及被指殺害沙特裔記者卡舒吉（Jamal Khashoggi）後，王儲穆罕默德就請來Consulum為該國策劃形象工程；該公司的其他政府客戶包括巴林及東非國家吉布提，都是被視為由獨裁政權統治的國家。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200629&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61110555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200629%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61110555&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=b06d8960\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200629%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61110555&h=e60eb0ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200629&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61110555</a>"},{"pid":"44f36056fcc6985431318266b18259447a85d69a","tid":2084983,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"港共淪落到咁，已經係我地最好既PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW內文有講間野創辦人，前身既PR公司係會利用大量SOCIAL MEDIA ACCOUNT帶風向，大家TWITTER FB REDDIT 唔好懶"},{"pid":"33399351ba3bdf2298cfb7b97dee1196f15ffc3d","tid":2084983,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06